text: Herman Witzig (December 5, 1907 - November 28, 1944) was an American gymnast. He competed in seven events at the 1928 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1907 births Category:1944 deaths Category:American male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of the United States Category:Gymnasts at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from New York City
